Nigiar Rustamovna (DP Coordinator)}\cell\row\pard \trowd\trql\trleft0\ltrrow\trpaddft3\trpaddt0\trpaddfl3\trpaddl0\trpaddfb3\trpaddb0\trpaddfr3\trpaddr0\clpadfl3\clpadl200\cellx1800\clpadfl3\clpadl200\cellx9638\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\kerning1\cf0\rtlch\af9\afs24\alang1040\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1040\dbch\af6\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1040\intbl\sl220\slmult0\ql\sb250\sa0{\cf18\f4\fs16
About me}\cell\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\kerning1\cf0\rtlch\af9\afs24\alang1040\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1040\dbch\af6\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1040\intbl\sl260\slmult0\ql\sb250\sa0{\f4\fs18
Before teaching Business Management in DP, I worked for 30 years as Senior Project Manager for international companies in the manufacturing, banking and consulting sectors; I have a broad range of experiences and know how in accounting, operations, logistics and marketing.\line My strong characteristics are: excellent time management skills, organizational skills, stress resistance and strong orientation to the result; I welcome new challenges and I am always looking for improvements. In my year of teaching I have refined my teaching technique, allowing me to finish the DP BM curriculum in one year and a half, leaving to students 4 months for the preparation to the exams. As a DP Core Coordinator, I managed to have all the DP students complete their EEs during the first DP year; with the most motivated students I managed to also to have their CAS completed during the first DP year. \line I consider efficiency and quality two non-negotiable prerequisites; thus beside by efficiency, I can say that my students have a 99% pass rate and 70% of them received grades between 5 and 7.\line During these years of teaching I was also able to improve my pastoral care skills; as a homeroom teacher I dealt with problematic students and I managed to improve their general behavior and to earn their respect; in one occasion, due to a temporary absence of the pastoral coordinator, I had to step in for a month, and deal with issues related to safeguarding.\line Due to my previous working experience, I have consolidated skills in managing people and teams of diverse nationalities; I have an eye for business process optimization and for budget saving. During my 10 years in teaching I seldom witnessed the above mentioned skills in schools' managers, and that makes me confident to be fully able to cover roles as Headteacher\u8198\'20 \u8198\'20 or school's director.}\cell\row\pard \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\kerning1\cf0\rtlch\af9\afs24\alang1040\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1040\dbch\af6\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1040\ql\f4

{\f4\par}}